title: Ewallet 6
description:
eWallet (Professional Edition) for Windows Mobile Smartphones


Avoid the danger of losing important information. Store your credit cards, passwords, PINs, calling cards, accounts, usernames and much more on your Smartphone. Your information is convenient for you, but encrypted for complete safety. Sync to your desktop for extra ease-of-use and backup. eWallet is simply the best and easiest personal information manager for your Smartphone. It includes customizable icons and templates, AutoPass instant password entry, and an easy-to-use interface.

Features include:

Built-in password generator 
Import tool for easy data entry 
Password hint 
Quality live technical support 
Complete synchronization between your desktop and Smartphone
